creator: Coders Hub
descriptionHtml:
FM Radio app provides you to access FM radio stations online without using headphone or location problem. Play your favorite channel & enjoy listening music anytime, anywhere in the world. The app has a beautiful user interface and easy to use.

Channels are categorized by all Indian languages or famous common words. Easy to browse, search and play. Most all Indian stations are available in the app and if you would like to add more stations than simply you can contact us and we will update channels.

FM Radio app uses best player to play channels with low internet connection as well. The app has very nice audio visualization, which make you feel very awesome when you see the main player page.

Now you can earn money daily too...

FM Radio app has multiple categories for FM channels so that every Indian can enjoy music in own languages:-

1. Hindi Radios
2. Tamil Radios
3. Malayalam Radios
4. Bollywood Radios
5. Telugu Radios
6. Kannada Radios
7. Punjabi Radios
8. Bangla Radios
9. English Radios
10. Sports & News Radios
11. Marathi, Gujarati, Others

Mostly all famous radio stations like Radio Mirchi, Big FM, Radio City, Fiver 104, etc. are available in the app and Equalizer to enhance music tuning.

Equalizer and FM Videos make this app unique and you can enjoy with your favorite FM Radios by listening or watching audio/video.

You can listen music in the background as well and use other apps while enjoying music. You can set the timer to stop currently playing radio station, which is helpful for night music lover.

Just download it and we are sure you will love this app. Share app with other and provide your feedback please. You can connect with us via mail info@coders-hub.com or visit our site www.coders-hub.com
